---
import BaseHead from '../../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import Tooltip from '../../components/Tooltip.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION, COMMENTS } from '../../config';
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-us">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
        <script data-isso={COMMENTS}
        src={COMMENTS + "js/embed.min.js"}></script>
	</head>
    <body>
        <Header />
        <center><prlgm class="text-2xl font-bold"><span>FRONTEND LIST</span></prlgm></center>
        <section>
            <p>
                Privacy and open source are two pillars of the internet -
                ones that are being taken away. Multiple companies and
                services are constantly trying to fight against them, which
                is why I'm throwing my own hat into the ring.
            </p>

            <br/>

            <p>
                Below is a list of frontends currently being hosted by
                yours truly. They are all unmodified, non-tracking, and
                completely community driven. The current list is small,
                but with your support, not only will there be a complete
                hosting list, but multiple locations will be selectable.
            </p>

            <br/>

            <p>
                Please comment below on any improvements I could do, or
                any problems you're getting. (Though please note that
                if it's a bug directly from the software, you'll need to
                report it to the developers, not me.) I'll also be making
                a server / chatroom soon for this.
            </p>

            <br/>

            <p>
                <b>Also, pro tip:</b> All links can be replaced with a
                shorthand version.

                <br/>

                Example: <code>qc1.iv.ggtyler.dev</code> -&gt; <code>qc1.iv.ggt.bz</code>
            </p>
            
            <p>
                Also - services are auto-restarted and updated every hour.
                Unless specified, they are using Docker builds, which are
                usually ready for production, and thus should not have any
                problems.
            </p>
        </section>
        <section class="text-center">
            <h1 class="text-2xl">Current Status: <prlgm><span><b>NOMINAL</b></span></prlgm></h1>
            Check back here for maintenence notices.
        </section>
        <cards class="text-center">
            <card class="h-auto">
                <span class="text-[3.5em]"><icon></icon>┊<icon></icon></span>
                <h1 class="text-xl"><a href="https://iv.ggtyler.dev">Invidious</a></h1>
                <center>(For YouTube)</center>
                <a href="https://github.com/iv-org/invidious"><icon></icon></a>
                <a href="https://invidious.io"><icon></icon></a>
                <hr/>
                <a href="https://qc1.iv.ggtyler.dev">QC-1 🇨🇦</a><br/>
                SEA-1 🇺🇸 (SOON™)
            </card>
            <card class="h-auto">
                <span class="text-[3.5em]"><icon></icon>┊<icon></icon></span>
                <h1 class="text-xl"><a href="https://nt.ggtyler.dev">Nitter</a></h1>
                <center>(For Twitter)</center>
                <a href="https://github.com/zedeus/nitter"><icon></icon></a>
                <hr/>
                <a href="https://qc1.nt.ggtyler.dev">QC-1 🇨🇦</a><br/>
                SEA-1 🇺🇸 (SOON™)
            </card>
            <card class="h-auto">
                <span class="text-[3.5em]"><icon></icon>┊<icon></icon></span>
                <h1 class="text-xl"><a href="https://td.ggtyler.dev">Teddit</a></h1>
                <center>(For Reddit)</center>
                <a href="https://codeberg.org/teddit/teddit"><icon></icon></a>
                <hr/>
                <a href="https://qc1.td.ggtyler.dev">QC-1 🇨🇦</a><br/>
                SEA-1 🇺🇸 (SOON™)
            </card>
            <card class="h-auto">
                <span class="text-[3.5em]"><icon></icon>┊<icon></icon></span>
                <h1 class="text-xl"><a href="https://lr.ggtyler.dev">LibReddit</a></h1>
                <center>(For Reddit)</center>
                <a href="https://github.com/libreddit/libreddit/"><icon></icon></a>
                <hr/>
                <a href="https://qc1.lr.ggtyler.dev">QC-1 🇨🇦</a><br/>
                SEA-1 🇺🇸 (SOON™)
            </card>
            <card class="h-auto">
                <span class="text-[3.5em]"><icon></icon>┊<icon></icon></span>
                <h1 class="text-xl"><a href="https://breeze.ggtyler.dev">Breezewiki</a></h1>
                <center>(For Fandom)</center>
                <a href="https://gitdab.com/cadence/breezewiki"><icon></icon></a>
                <Tooltip text="This service runs on the Docker version (from PussTheCat.org)"/>
                <hr/>
                <a href="https://qc1.breeze.ggtyler.dev">QC-1 🇨🇦</a><br/>
                <a href="https://sea1.breeze.ggtyler.dev">SEA-1 🇺🇸</a>
            </card>
        </cards>
        <br/>
        <section id="isso-thread">
            <noscript>JavaScript needs to be activated to view comments.</noscript>
        </section>
        <Footer />
    </body>
</html>